description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Gatinho purrs with a rating of 54, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 270, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, 5 for East, Box for South, and Stringalong for West. Gatinho has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/50545-15472-2.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gatinho [270 Votes, Hall of Fame]
